  <entry>
    <title>Git常用操作</title>
    <link href="/2025/08/18/git/"/>
    <url>/2025/08/18/git/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="Git常用操作"><a href="#Git常用操作" class="headerlink" title="Git常用操作"></a>Git常用操作</h2><h3 id="本地分支推送远程"><a href="#本地分支推送远程" class="headerlink" title="本地分支推送远程"></a>本地分支推送远程</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">git add .<br>git commit -m <span class="hljs-string">&quot;commit message&quot;</span><br>git push origin 远程分支名<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="删除本地分支（branch）"><a href="#删除本地分支（branch）" class="headerlink" title="删除本地分支（branch）"></a>删除本地分支（branch）</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash"><span class="hljs-comment"># 查看本地的所有分支</span><br>git branch <br><br><span class="hljs-comment"># 删除指定本地分支（-D 表示强制删除）</span><br>git branch -d 本地分支名<br><br><span class="hljs-comment"># 修改当前所在分支的名称（当前分支）</span><br>git branch -m 新分支名<br><br><span class="hljs-comment"># 修改指定分支的名称（不要求当前在该分支）</span><br>git branch -m 旧分支名 新分支名<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="删除远程分支"><a href="#删除远程分支" class="headerlink" title="删除远程分支"></a>删除远程分支</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">git push origin --delete 远程分支名<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="推送到远程分支"><a href="#推送到远程分支" class="headerlink" title="推送到远程分支"></a>推送到远程分支</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash"><span class="hljs-comment"># 当你创建了一个全新的本地分支，需要把它推送到远程仓库(建立追踪关系)</span><br>git push -u origin 本地分支名<br><br><span class="hljs-comment"># 推送已有分支的提交内容</span><br><span class="hljs-comment"># 已建立追踪关系后</span><br>git push<br><span class="hljs-comment"># 未建立追踪关系</span><br>git push origin 本地分支名<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="合并其他分支的内容"><a href="#合并其他分支的内容" class="headerlink" title="合并其他分支的内容"></a>合并其他分支的内容</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash"><span class="hljs-comment"># 获取远程仓库（默认origin）中所有分支最新的信息，但不会自动合并或更新本地分支</span><br>git fetch origin<br><br><span class="hljs-comment"># 将远程分支最新的信息合并到当前分支</span><br>git merge origin/分支名<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="撤回提交"><a href="#撤回提交" class="headerlink" title="撤回提交"></a>撤回提交</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash"><span class="hljs-comment"># 撤销最后一次提交并保留更改</span><br>git reset --soft HEAD～1<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="暂存-stash"><a href="#暂存-stash" class="headerlink" title="暂存 stash"></a>暂存 stash</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash"><span class="hljs-comment"># 未提交的代码保存至堆栈区（暂存区）</span><br>git stash save <span class="hljs-string">&quot;保存的名字&quot;</span><br><br><span class="hljs-comment"># 查看暂存区的所有列表</span><br>git stash list <br><br><span class="hljs-comment"># 把当前最新存进去的一个取出来</span><br>git stash pop <br><br><span class="hljs-comment"># 用于取指定名称的暂存（不会从暂存删除，需手动删除）</span><br>git stash apply stash@名称（stash@&#123;1&#125;）<br><br><span class="hljs-comment"># 删除指定名称的暂存</span><br>git stash drop stash@名称（stash@&#123;1&#125;）<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="cherry-pick（将某个或某几个提交commit，复制到当前分支）"><a href="#cherry-pick（将某个或某几个提交commit，复制到当前分支）" class="headerlink" title="cherry-pick（将某个或某几个提交commit，复制到当前分支）"></a>cherry-pick（将某个或某几个提交commit，复制到当前分支）</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash"><span class="hljs-comment"># 以简洁的单行格式，查看分支的提交历史</span><br>git <span class="hljs-built_in">log</span> 本地分支名(feature/old) --oneline<br><br><span class="hljs-comment"># 类似输出格式</span><br>a1b2c3d 修复视频播放<br>d4e5f6g 优化曝光统计<br>h7i8j9k 重构推荐流<br><br><span class="hljs-comment"># 将提交 a1b2c3d 的改动应用到当前分支</span><br>git cherry-pick a1b2c3d<br><span class="hljs-comment"># 挑选多个提交（按顺序）</span><br>git cherry-pick a1b2c3d d4e5f6g h7i8j9k<br><span class="hljs-comment"># 从 A 到 B 之间的所有提交（不包含 A）</span><br>git cherry-pick a1b2c3d..e4f5g6h<br><span class="hljs-comment"># 从 A 到 B 之间的所有提交（包含 A）</span><br>git cherry-pick a1b2c3d^..e4f5g6h<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="Rebase-交互式操作"><a href="#Rebase-交互式操作" class="headerlink" title="Rebase 交互式操作"></a>Rebase 交互式操作</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash"><span class="hljs-comment"># 进入交互式变基（n = 操作最近的 n 个提交）</span><br>git rebase -i HEAD~n<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="常用操作（在-vim-编辑器中）"><a href="#常用操作（在-vim-编辑器中）" class="headerlink" title="常用操作（在 vim 编辑器中）"></a>常用操作（在 vim 编辑器中）</h4><table><thead><tr><th>操作</th><th>将 <code>pick</code> 改为</th><th>说明</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>压缩节点</td><td><code>squash</code> &#x2F; <code>fixup</code></td><td><code>s</code> 保留提交信息，<code>f</code> 丢弃</td></tr><tr><td>修改备注</td><td><code>reword</code></td><td>保存后会弹出新编辑器修改信息</td></tr><tr><td>调整顺序</td><td>移动行位置</td><td>直接拖动 <code>pick</code> 开头的行</td></tr><tr><td>删除节点</td><td><code>drop</code></td><td>或直接删除该行</td></tr></tbody></table><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash"><span class="hljs-comment"># vim 保存退出：Esc → :wq</span><br><span class="hljs-comment"># 放弃操作：Esc → :q!</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
    
